# Design System Rules

- Read docs/design/DESIGN_REFERENCE.md before writing any React component
- Open docs/design/prototype-v4.html to see the target visual output
- Use only Tailwind colour tokens from src/index.css @theme — no hardcoded hex
- Dark mode surface hierarchy:
    bg-background-dark (#1B1D21) — page background
    bg-panel-dark      (#23262B) — panel/card surface
    border-border-dark (#2D3139) — all borders
- Active state: bg-primary/10 text-primary (tinted, not solid)
- Primary buttons only: bg-primary text-white
- font-display for UI text, font-mono for all code content
- All icons use Material Symbols Outlined
- Category icons defined in src/constants/library.ts categoryIcons
- Import sidebarMapping, gridRoleMapping, categorySubtitles from
  src/constants/library.ts — never redefine them in a component
